{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "10.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "timeseries",
      "name": "Time series",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "stat",
      "name": "Stat",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "gauge",
      "name": "Gauge",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "piechart",
      "name": "Pie chart",
      "version": ""
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "uid": "krab-main",
  "title": "Krab — Main Dashboard",
  "description": "Главный dashboard Краба: health, LLM routing, memory retrieval (C6), swarm, errors, ops.",
  "tags": [
    "krab",
    "observability"
  ],
  "timezone": "",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": "",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Row 1 — Health",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Krab uptime",
      "description": "time() - process_start_time_seconds. Сбрасывается при рестарте userbot.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 60
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 300
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "time() - process_start_time_seconds{job=\"krab_owner_panel\"}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Metrics freshness",
      "description": "Возраст последнего сбора /metrics. Если > 120с — Prometheus не скрапит Krab.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 60
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 120
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "time() - krab_metrics_generated_at"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "LLM route status",
      "description": "krab_llm_route_ok (1=ok, 0=error). Берём max по меткам provider/model.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "ERROR",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "OK",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(krab_llm_route_ok)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Row 2 — LLM + Routing",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "LLM request rate per provider",
      "description": "rate(krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_count) by provider — число завершённых LLM-запросов в секунду.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (provider) (rate(krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_count[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "LLM route errors per provider",
      "description": "krab_llm_route_ok == 0 по времени — считаем провайдеры, которые сейчас в ошибке.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 40
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count by (provider) (krab_llm_route_ok == 0)",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active LLM route (provider/model)",
      "description": "Последний активный маршрут — чей статус == ok.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 8
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "name",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "krab_llm_route_ok == 1",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{model}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "LLM route latency P50 / P90 / P99",
      "description": "histogram_quantile по krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_bucket.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 5
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by (le, provider) (rate(krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P50 {{provider}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.9, sum by (le, provider) (rate(krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P90 {{provider}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le, provider) (rate(krab_llm_route_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P99 {{provider}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24
      },
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Row 3 — Memory Retrieval (C6)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Retrieval mode distribution",
      "description": "krab_memory_retrieval_mode_total by mode (fts/vec/hybrid/none).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": [
            "value",
            "percent"
          ]
        },
        "pieType": "donut",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (mode) (krab_memory_retrieval_mode_total)",
          "legendFormat": "{{mode}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Retrieval latency P50 / P90 / P99 per phase",
      "description": "histogram_quantile по krab_memory_retrieval_latency_seconds_bucket (phase = fts/vec/mmr/total).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 25
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 5
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by (le, phase) (rate(krab_memory_retrieval_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P50 {{phase}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.9, sum by (le, phase) (rate(krab_memory_retrieval_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P90 {{phase}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le, phase) (rate(krab_memory_retrieval_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P99 {{phase}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Archive DB size",
      "description": "krab_archive_db_size_bytes. Threshold 1 GiB.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 25
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 2147483648,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 536870912
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1073741824
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "krab_archive_db_size_bytes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 33
      },
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Row 4 — Swarm + Tools",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Swarm per-team tool blocks",
      "description": "rate(krab_swarm_tool_blocked_total) by team.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 40
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (team) (rate(krab_swarm_tool_blocked_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{team}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Top commands (rate 5m)",
      "description": "topk(10, rate(krab_command_invocations_total[5m])).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 34
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (command) (rate(krab_command_invocations_total[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "!{{command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 42
      },
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Row 5 — Errors + Ops",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error digest fires",
      "description": "rate(krab_error_digest_fired_total) by outcome (ok/empty/failed).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 43
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 40
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (outcome) (rate(krab_error_digest_fired_total[15m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{outcome}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Auto-restart attempts",
      "description": "rate(krab_auto_restart_attempts_total[10m]) — должно быть ~0 в стабильном контуре.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 43
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 40
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(krab_auto_restart_attempts_total[10m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Memory validator — injections blocked",
      "description": "rate(krab_memory_validator_injection_blocked_total[1h]) — prompt-injection attempts остановленные при сохранении memory.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 43
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(krab_memory_validator_injection_blocked_total[1h])",
          "legendFormat": "injections/hr"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Memory validator pending",
      "description": "krab_memory_validator_pending — подтверждений в очереди (alert > 15).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 51
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 15
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "krab_memory_validator_pending"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Reminders pending",
      "description": "krab_reminders_pending_total — напоминания в очереди.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 51
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "krab_reminders_pending_total"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Guest LLM skips (security)",
      "description": "Суммарные пропуски LLM-ответов гостям в группах (ACL).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 51
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(krab_guest_llm_skipped_total)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 55
      },
      "id": 60,
      "title": "Row — Sentry Performance (external links)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "LLM call P95 (Sentry)",
      "description": "External link to Sentry Performance tab filtered by transaction.op:llm.call. Healthy: P95 < 10s.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 56
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### LLM latency (Sentry Performance)\n\n**op:** `llm.call` — per-request span around `openclaw_<model>` stream.\n\n**Healthy:** P95 < 10s, P50 < 3s.\n\n[Open in Sentry](https://po-zm.sentry.io/performance/?project=4511254217818192&query=transaction.op%3Allm.call&statsPeriod=24h)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Memory retrieval P95 (Sentry)",
      "description": "External link to Sentry Performance tab filtered by transaction.op:memory.retrieval. Healthy: P95 < 100ms.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 56
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Memory retrieval latency (Sentry Performance)\n\n**op:** `memory.retrieval` — HybridRetriever.search with sub-spans `memory.fts`, `memory.vec`, `memory.mmr`.\n\n**Healthy:** P95 < 100ms, P50 < 30ms.\n\n[Open in Sentry](https://po-zm.sentry.io/performance/?project=4511254217818192&query=transaction.op%3Amemory.retrieval&statsPeriod=24h)"
      }
    }
  ]
}